library(tidyverse)

questions <- read_csv("questions.csv")

-- Column specification -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
cols(
  id = col_double(),
  creation_date = col_date(format = ""),
  score = col_double()
)
answers <- read_csv("answers.csv")

-- Column specification -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
cols(
  id = col_double(),
  creation_date = col_date(format = ""),
  question_id = col_double(),
  score = col_double()
)
tags <- read_csv("tags.csv")

-- Column specification -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
cols(
  id = col_double(),
  tag_name = col_character()
)
question_tags <- read_csv("question_tags.csv")

-- Column specification -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
cols(
  question_id = col_double(),
  tag_id = col_double()
)
